 4.Students below 10 years of age; the scale uses the BIA Bioelectrical method to contact the foot through the ITO conductive coating, sending a weak current to circulate in the body. The FAT does not conduct electricity, the muscle conducts electricity, and it is displayed on your phone by detecting the resistance value. And the above crowd is not suitable because, the detection process of the user's body has a certain impact factors, resulting in abnormal detection results. (such as: pregnant women with amniotic fluid, fetal, etc., will affect the BIA detection of the accuracy of the data.)

