1.Into the “Mine” interface, click on the Fitbit bar, into the Fitbit interface;

2.Open the Fitbit switch button, will jump to the Fitbit login interface, enter the registered Fitbit account number and password (or in the interface Drop-down Select registration Fitbit);

3.After the successful login to return to the Fitbit interface, at this time Fitbit switch button state for “Open”, the connection Fitbit success;

4After measurement, the data will be uploaded to Fitbit, you can log on to open Fitbit app or login Fitbit Web page to view relevant data.
